---
description: FIELD-O engineering standards
globs:
  - "src/**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Use TypeScript-first patterns.

Preferred standards:
- modular feature-based architecture
- separate UI from business logic
- separate persistence from rendering
- keep components focused
- avoid oversized files
- avoid hidden side effects
- keep translation strings centralized
- keep report logic typed and explicit
- document major architectural changes in docs/tech/

Do not add new functionality by bloating App.tsx further.
Refactor into modules when extending the product.

